text: Russell Prescott is a Republican member of the Executive Council of New Hampshire, representing the 3rd district since 2016. Prescott is a former member of the New Hampshire Senate, representing the 23rd district from 2010–2016.*Dinan, Elizabeth (September 14, 2016), "Prescott, Roth win Executive Council primaries", Seacoastonline.com ==References== Category:Members of the New Hampshire Executive Council Category:New Hampshire Republicans Category:New Hampshire state senators Category:People from Kingston, New Hampshire
